{"text_id":211736,"tokens":["How"," to"," Clean"," Smoke"," Damage",":"," A"," Step","-","by","-","Step"," Guide","\n","Dealing"," with"," smoke"," damage"," in"," your"," home"," can"," be"," a"," daunting"," task",","," but"," it","'","s"," essential"," to"," take"," the"," right"," steps"," to"," clean"," it"," up"," properly","."," Follow"," these"," simple"," steps"," to"," clean"," smoke"," damage"," and"," restore"," your"," home"," to"," its"," former"," state",".","\n","Part"," ","1",":"," Preparing"," to"," Clean"," Smoke"," Damage","\n","1","."," Get"," permission"," from"," a"," fire"," marshal"," to"," safely"," re","-","enter"," your"," home","."," Don","'","t"," re","-","enter"," a"," home"," that"," has"," been"," damaged"," by"," smoke"," until"," a"," fire"," marshal"," has"," deemed"," it"," safe"," to"," do"," so",".","\n","2","."," Allow"," fresh"," air"," to"," circulate","."," Open"," doors"," and"," windows"," to"," let"," fresh"," air"," into"," your"," home",".","\n","3","."," Dry"," wet"," items"," before"," attempting"," to"," clean"," smoke"," damage","."," Wet"," items"," can"," spread"," soot"," and"," make"," the"," damage"," worse","."," Use"," a"," de","humid","ifier"," or"," fans"," to"," dry"," out"," your"," home"," before"," cleaning",".","\n","Part"," ","2",":"," Cleaning"," Smoke"," Damage","\n","4","."," Ensure"," the"," area"," is"," properly"," ventilated","."," Wear"," a"," protective"," mask"," and"," ensure"," that"," there"," is"," an"," adequate"," airflow"," before"," you"," start"," cleaning",".","\n","5","."," Wear"," safety"," goggles"," and"," heavy","-","duty"," gloves"," to"," protect"," yourself"," from"," the"," smoke"," and"," chemicals"," used"," in"," the"," cleaning"," process",".","\n","6","."," Place"," a"," drop","-","cloth"," on"," the"," floor"," to"," protect"," against"," spills"," and"," drips",".","\n","7","."," Get"," rid"," of"," loose"," soot"," on"," the"," surface"," of"," the"," walls"," by"